OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry at first
OL,6,Fwith some hazy evening sunshine. It
OL,7,Fwill gradually cloud over from the
OL,8,Fnorth through the evening and
OL,9,Fovernight with the odd spot of light
OL,10,Frain.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA cloudy start with some
OL,13,Fpatchy light rain possible. Staying
OL,14,Flargely cloudy through the day but
OL,15,Fperhaps brightening up somewhat as
OL,16,Fcloud starts to break at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
